      "styleName": "Double Happiness Banquet",
      "visualDNA": "Imperial banquet — lacquer red means joy, gilt gold means wealth. Deep lacquer-red chrome with gilt hairlines and a 囍 double-happiness medallion, warm porcelain ground, Ming-style Noto Serif SC type, hongbao-red guest cards. Ceremonial, warm, handcrafted.",
